    "keywords" -> {"Rabi oscillation"}, "specialkeywords" -> {}, 
    "tutorialcollectionlinks" -> {}, "index" -> True, "label" -> 
    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "CommutatorFree4[mat, {{t1, t2, ..., tn}}] represents a sequence of \
propagators (i.e., the time-ordered evolution operator) at time steps tk \
governed by the time-dependent Hamiltonian matrix mat[t],where mat is a \
function that gives an Hermitian matrix for a numeric value of t. \
CommutatorFree4[mat, {t, min, max, dt}] is equivalent to CommutatorFree4[mat, \
Range[min, max, (max - min)/100]. CommutatorFree4[mat, {t, min, max}] is \
equivalent to CommutatorFree4[mat, {t, min, max, 1}]. CommutatorFree4[mat, \
{t, max}] is equivalent to CommutatorFree4[mat, {t, 0, max, 1}].", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "CommutatorFree4", 
